          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "\"Otonono barrilé”\nChorus\nOtonono barrilé  \n(Otonono, barrel drum)\n\nVerses\nOtonono, long live my people\nOtonono, dance it well\nMy dada, my dadinué\nOtonono barrilé\nSo they’ll play my barrel drums\n\nOtonono, long live my people\nOtonono, dance it well\nMy dada, my dadinué\nOtonono barrilé\nSo they’ll play my barrel drums"
